nhc_headline: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE MOVING AWAY FROM THE AZORES...
summary: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE MOVING AWAY FROM THE AZORES... As of 12:00 PM GMT Fri Sep 26 the center of Gabrielle was located near 39.8, -24.2 with movement ENE at 29 mph. The minimum central pressure was 992 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
